					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-12090689#post-4409568</guid>
				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-12090689/scp-4841#post-4409568</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Tue, 29 Oct 2019 16:56:21 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Imperios</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>2019329</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Minor nitpick: if you want to describe where the village is located, you should mention the federal subject, not the district. Districts in Russia are second-level administrative divisions, similar to American counties, and often have identical names in different regions.</p> <p>Just say the village is in Krasnoyarsk Krai, it will convey more information for anyone familiar with Russia.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
